-- Fairfax Financial profit jumps on investments
-- By Cameron French
-- Thu May 01, 2014 05:13PM EDT
-- None



TORONTO, May 1 (Reuters) - Fairfax Financial Holdings <FFH.TO>, the Canadian property and casualty insurer run by investment guru Prem Watsa, said its first-quarter profit more than quadrupled due to strong investment gains and improved underwriting results.

